# .env.example
# Copy this file to .env and fill in values as needed.
# No secrets are required to run the MVP scaffold.

# --- Future use only ---
# API keys, database URLs, and other secrets will be added here
# when the tool moves beyond the MVP prototype stage.
# Do not commit a populated .env file to version control.

# Example placeholders (not used in current build):
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your-key-here
# DATABASE_URL=your-db-url-here
# APP_SECRET_KEY=your-secret-here
